== Bangogo ==

Bisina ya bangogo ya Kituba kele [[kikongo]], [[lingala]], [[kiyaka]], [[kiyansi]], [[kiswahili]], [[kifalanse]] ye [[kiputugali]].

=== Minoko ya kifalanse ===

*falangi (''franc'')
*kaminio (''camion'')
*kaye (''cahier'')
*leta (''l'état'')
*sose (''sauce'')
*tono (''tonneau'')
*watu (''ouate'')

=== Minoko ya kiputugali ===

*kilapi (''lápis'')
*kumbi (''comboio'')
*mapa (''mapa'')
*misa (''missa'')
*Mputu (''Portugal'')
*numelo (''número'')
*sikoti (''chicotte'')

=== Minoko ya kiswahili ===

*langi (''rangi'')
*matata (''matata'')
*sanduku (''sanduku'')
*simba (''simba'' = nkosi)

